Package: CAOP.RAA.2024
Title: Official Administrative Map of the Azores (CAOP 2024)
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ramiro", "Magno", , "rmagno@pattern.institute", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5226-3441")),
    person("Pattern Institute", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Provides the official administrative boundaries of the Azores 
    (Região Autónoma dos Açores (RAA)) as defined in the 2024 edition of the 
    Carta Administrativa Oficial de Portugal (CAOP), published by the 
    Direção-Geral do Território (DGT). The package includes convenience
    functions to import these boundaries as 'sf' objects for spatial analysis in
    R.
    Source: <https://geo2.dgterritorio.gov.pt/caop/CAOP_RAA_2024-gpkg.zip>.
